name: Gradsters.github.io
body:
### A marketplace of master projects, PhD, post-PhD and internships.
Gradsters is the one-stop source to find graduate research projects and internships

### Find talent
At the same time, we offer researchers a chance to find, connect, and recruit prospective students that best match their needs

### Push Boundaries
We believe in the power of curiosity and discoveries through collaborative higher education. At Gradsters, we create a community and a market place where every available position is filled with the right talent.
